Package game.environment

Class Lake

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.engine.Ground
game.environment.Lake
All Implemented Interfaces:
Capable, Printable, GroundInterface
public class Lake
extends Ground
Class creation of the Lake object. The lake object will contain instances of Fish as an available food source within the world. It will also contain sips for dinosaurs to drink from.

    • tick

      public void tick​(Location location)
      Tick updates the current turn of game for the class object. Every turn, there is a possibility for a new fish to be added to the lake if it is not full. In addition, every 10 turns it checks if there is rainfall based on a probability, and if there is, it will increase the number of sips in the lake.
      Overrides:
      tick in class Ground
      Parameters:
      location - The location of the Ground
